{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_8_level_main_08-06_end","storyGroup":"main_8","storySort":14,"storyDependence":"main_8_level_main_08-06_beg","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"R8-6","storyName":"战场，蔓延不止","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"爱国者首次对塔露拉表露他的意见，斥责塔露拉是空想。塔露拉捡到了名叫萨沙与伊诺的孩子，阿丽娜提醒塔露拉不要忘记最初的坚持。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_08-06_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_08-06","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":12,"next":14,"characters":["塔露拉","爱国者","霜星","？？？","怯生生的孩子","萨沙","阿丽娜"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"character","id":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e1/Avg_bg_bg_snow_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":6},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":8,"musicid":0},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":10},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"谢谢您的支援，先生......","id":11,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"——塔露拉。","id":13,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你想离开雪原？你会被乌萨斯的铁甲碾碎。","id":14,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"爸？为什么是现在？我们不是打赢了——","id":16,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_1505_frstar_10.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"盾卫已经去收集资源。你收队。命令全部人转移。","id":18,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"......是。","id":20,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_1505_frstar_10.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你和你的计划会让所有人都送命。","id":22,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"text","text":"塔露拉意识到，面前的巨人是第一次对自己发表他的意见。即使这意见不可撼动，伤人入骨。","id":23},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"西北冻原也不能让我们活下去。我们的队伍越壮大，就越需要食物与能源补给，厌恶我们的聚落远比支持我们的村庄更多。","id":25,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"一年一季的苔麦......哪怕我们也参与耕种，那能收成多少？","id":26,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我们的田地会不会被纠察队毁掉？游击队能够轻松地战胜他们，但其他的感染者做不到。","id":27,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你在加速他们的死亡。","id":29,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我们只有离开冻原。不是去萨米，也不是去荒地......我们向东方去，向南方去，向温暖的地方去。","id":31,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你要怎么样生存下去？ 你要怎样让我们这么多人生存下去？","id":33,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"游击队是在救人。游击队绝不会牺牲游击队之外的人。只有战士才牺牲。","id":34,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"然而，在各个城市和城市周边生活的感染者，远比在冻原上的更多。","id":36,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"您常驻守北方，对北方感染者的遭遇深恶痛绝......所以您也不太有机会了解到，南方的感染者是怎样生活的。","id":37,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","id":38},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"他们过得很好？","id":39,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"他们过得很糟。","id":41,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你想吸纳他们。","id":43,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我要团结他们。","id":45,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"帝国看向感染者时，你首当其冲。","id":47,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"不是团结在我身边。不。是团结在同一个理念周围。","id":49,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"理念？感染者在冻原上被当作锯末，在矿场里被当作废渣，在聚落被当作惩示，在城市被当作什么燃料。","id":51,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"冻原上的感染者既不无知也不愚蠢。我们不抱幻想。所有的理念在被实践前都是幻想。","id":52,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"冻原上还有矿场，有巡逻队，有愚蠢懈怠的守军。我们有地方获得资源。","id":53,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"冰原上的资源迟早会被耗尽，因为我们没有开发资源的手段。","id":55,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我们没有可持久运作的移动城市，我们没有称职专业的天灾信使......","id":56,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"走向城市，我们一无所有。","id":58,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":59},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我们会获得新的朋友。","id":60,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"谁是你的朋友？","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我可以承认你的计划有过人之处。","id":63,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"然而，你所图谋的，即使有可取之处也不出奇。","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"有多少战略家在冻原上潦倒而死？你所说的这些，我看不出你为何能做到，靠什么去实现。","id":65,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"为什么先皇能让大地颤抖？因为他执着于此，且从不谈论远大愿景。他只迈步。","id":66,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"而你不能。","id":67,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......","id":69,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"先生！","id":70,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你说我会被乌萨斯的铁甲碾碎，我承认，他们迟早会看向我们这里。我们总有一天会被抓到。我们都逃不过。","id":71,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"“让他们来”？您会这样想吗，先生？","id":72,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"冻原会让您更好地准备一场决战吗？","id":73,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"你在寻找一个新的战场？","id":75,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我在找寻一个胜机。","id":77,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"对于更多感染者来说那是希望。但对于你我这种战士，那是一个契机。摆脱我们固有战略的唯一契机。","id":78,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"在冻原上的辗转到头来也只是慢性死亡......就像我们身为感染者剩下的那点生命一样。我要不断重复这一点，因为你我都清楚。","id":79,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/53/Avg_avg_npc_078_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"——","id":81,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"我女儿也许会相信你。","id":82,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"但我不相信一个从没因事实而失望，一直只是在陈托某种假大空的学说的人。","id":83,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......","id":85,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":86},{"type":"character","id":87},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":88},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"塔露拉？你去哪里？","id":90,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_1505_frstar_10.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"没事的。只是去检查矿场有没有生还者。","id":92,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_1505_frstar_1#10","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"游击队已经带队出发，聚落也开始转移了。乌萨斯的军队也没有继续追踪我们的迹象......","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_1505_frstar_10.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"霜星","text":"爸？你怎么了？","id":95,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_char_1505_frstar_10.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_025_1#3","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"咳......","id":97,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"爱国者","text":"只是普通的咳嗽。","id":98,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/46/Avg_avg_npc_025_3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":99},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":100},{"type":"character","id":101},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":102},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":103},{"type":"text","text":"窸窣声","id":104},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"——","id":106,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"这里有人吗？","id":107,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......我知道你们在这。你们不是乌萨斯军人，你们连树枝都没踩断。","id":108,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我没有恶意。如果你们不是感染者，我也就此离开，除非你们需要帮助......","id":109,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"不，不准再靠近！","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"别动！否则我就放箭了！","id":112},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"啊。","id":114,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":115},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":116},{"type":"character","id":117},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/88/Avg_avg_8_5.png","x":"20","y":"0","xScale":"1.05","yScale":"1.05","fadetime":"0","id":118},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"20","yFrom":"0","xTo":"-20","yTo":"0","xScale":"1.05","yScale":"1.05","duration":"20","block":"false","id":119},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怯生生的孩子","text":"她，她是感染者！萨沙，我的法术能把感染者赶走的......！","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨沙","text":"不可以用法术！","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怯生生的孩子","text":"萨沙......","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨沙","text":"你，你快点走开！我们只是从矿场里拿了些东西......我们不想杀人！","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨沙","text":"我会放箭的！你会死！！","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怯生生的孩子","text":"萨沙......可是，可你说......","id":126},{"type":"dialog","id":127},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":128},{"type":"image","fadetime":"0","id":129},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":130},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......","id":132,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你们有几天没吃饭了？","id":133,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_085","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨沙","text":"不关你事！","id":135,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/12/Avg_avg_npc_085.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"在军驻矿场附近，你们也不敢生火。","id":137,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......你们抖得就像筛谷时的小麦。","id":138,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_084","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怯生生的孩子","text":"呜......","id":140,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/43/Avg_avg_npc_084.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_085","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨沙","text":"嘁。","id":142,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/12/Avg_avg_npc_085.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#2","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"不要怕。","id":144,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"character","id":145},{"type":"dialog","id":146},{"type":"text","text":"塔露拉用手抓住了一根树枝。","id":147},{"type":"text","text":"她轻轻将树枝递向两个孩子，树枝由内而外飘出火星。","id":148},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_084","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"怯生生的孩子","text":"啊......","id":150,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/43/Avg_avg_npc_084.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_085","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"萨沙","text":"你......","id":152,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/12/Avg_avg_npc_085.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_078#2","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"暖和些了吧。","id":154,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"对，我的确是感染者。","id":155,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":156},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":157},{"type":"character","id":158},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/2d/Avg_bg_bg_snowconutry_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":159},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":160},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":161},{"type":"dialog","id":162},{"type":"character","id":163},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"原来是这样。","id":165,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_079_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"你就是这样找到萨沙和伊诺......他们一直不愿意和别人说之前的事。","id":166,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_079_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"如果我们没发现他们，他们肯定活不下去的。","id":168,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"也许在爱国者否定我之后，只有这件事算是好事了。","id":169,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"那今天这个是怎么回事？","id":171,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......训练里我的法术不小心波及了霜星挂在旁边的斗篷。她要和我拼命。","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"你就答应她一定帮她缝好了？","id":175,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#3","focus":"2","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"事实上，阿丽娜......","id":177,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_npc_078_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#3","focus":"1","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"算了吧。给我吧，你对针线怕是一窍不通。","id":179,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你不想加入我们的队伍吗？也许加上你的伶牙俐齿，我说服爱国者的可能性更大些。","id":181,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我说过了，塔露拉......我说过的。我的法术对游击队没用。","id":183,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我可以沾上血，但我不想主动去伤害人。你以后可不单是会面对感染者纠察队。","id":184,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#3","focus":"2","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"那我当时拉着你一起走......也许太难为你了。","id":186,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_npc_078_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#3","focus":"1","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"啊，你故意这么说的，是不是？","id":188,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#3","focus":"2","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"没有，我......","id":190,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_npc_078_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#3","name2":"avg_npc_078#3","focus":"1","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"你可别记岔了，是我要跟着你走的。","id":192,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_079_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"走到现在，只有一个原因，是因为......塔露拉，我觉得你很可能会忘记。","id":193,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_079_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#3","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"忘记什么？","id":195,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"忘记自己到底要做什么。","id":197,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_079_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我一直在为了感染者的未来而努力。","id":199,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"你最开始不是这么说的。","id":201,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_079_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......","id":203,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"塔露拉，我们都知道人是会变的。","id":205,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_079_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"要是我们把自己坚持的东西都一点一点抛干净，或者换成新的东西的话，那是不是到某个时候，我们就其实没再坚持什么了呢？","id":206,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_079_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"在不断的战斗和这些事情的变化里，我肯定要改变方针的。僵化的思维会让我们变得脆弱。","id":208,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"可你顽固的部分在哪呢？","id":210,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_079_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"——","id":212,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"你是想证明，感染者和普通人一样，还是想证明，普通人和感染者一样呢？","id":214,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_079_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"有什么区别？","id":216,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"如果只有感染者，谁是普通人？我们是要让所有人都染上矿石病，还是让我们和普通人彻底隔绝呢？","id":218,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_079_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"而如果只有普通人，没有感染者......感染了矿石病的是普通人，没有感染的也是普通人。","id":219,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_079_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"神民是普通人，先民是普通人，同乡那样的农民是普通人，城里居住的人，也该是普通人。","id":220,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_079_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"塔露拉，你想回到家人身边吗？","id":221,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_079_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我的家人就是你们。","id":223,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"哎。不是。","id":225,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_079_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"如果去掉我们身上的矿石病......我们就能回家了吗？","id":226,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e5/Avg_avg_npc_079_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079#4","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我和你一样，也认为不能。","id":228,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"冻原和我们的生活彻底改变了我们。感染者已经无法重回他们过去的生活了。","id":229,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":230},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":231},{"type":"character","id":232},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e6/Avg_bg_bg_snowconutryinside.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":233},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":234},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":235},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"塔露拉，你现在还会因为自己是感染者而感到骄傲吗？","id":237,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"为什么这么问？","id":239,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"因为不用法杖就能施术？因为我们的生命是这样短暂？因为我们即使遭遇这么多困难，依然也会坚持活下去？","id":241,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"塔露拉，你会选哪个理由？","id":242,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我没必要选，阿丽娜。","id":244,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"作为一个感染者，我就是骄傲的。因为这片大地还没杀得了我。","id":245,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"顺带一提，我们要追求公平也不需要什么原因。因为我们本来就该追求公平。","id":246,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"如果这片大地不肯给，那我们就从它那拿回来。","id":247,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"那你是真的很勇敢了。","id":249,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你没在笑我吧。","id":251,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"没有，怎么会。","id":253,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"嗯，那......我觉得，是所有肯和这个强加在我们身上的命运斗争下去的人，都很勇敢。","id":255,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"那你一定觉得——","id":257,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"唔。","id":258,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"觉得什么？","id":260,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我们的命运很烂。","id":262,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"那当然。","id":264,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我不这么觉得，塔露拉。","id":266,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......你又在说反话了，阿丽娜。","id":268,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"不......我是说，我能坐在这里，能和你聊天，知道聚落外面有我们的战士正在守候，命运待我已经很好了。","id":270,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"可别这么说。命运是善妒的。你那么说，它指不定就把你说的这些都拿走了。","id":272,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"可我是不相信命运的，塔露拉。","id":274,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"因为你能改变它？","id":276,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"因为我看不见它。","id":278,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":279},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":280},{"type":"character","id":281},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/55/Avg_avg_8_4.png","x":"50","y":"0","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"0","id":282},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"50","yFrom":"0","xTo":"-50","yTo":"0","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","duration":"40","block":"false","id":283},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"塔露拉，看得见摸得着的事情是可靠的。","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我能看见自己手中的这件斗篷。我能看见烛光，能看见自己手中的针线。","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我能看见感染者孩子们的笑脸，我能看见烤得喷香的蔬菜上飘散出去的白色热气。","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我能看得见雪花，看得见夜空中两个月亮轻快的舞步。","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"而有的人连这些也看不见。","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"塔露拉，如果有一天我们都离开了你，你还能战斗下去吗？","id":290},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"这是什么话？","id":292,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"总会发生的。到那时候，你还会觉得所谓的命运值得你去抗争吗？","id":294,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"你会不会想，这太烂了，我已经什么都做不了了？","id":295,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"如果爱国者教会了我什么，那只有一点我觉得我已经学会了，而且早就学会了。","id":297,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我不会低头。","id":298,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"它嘲讽我，那我肯定会把它烧成灰。","id":299,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"好傻哦，塔露拉。除非你是个老头子。","id":301,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"喂！","id":303,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"老头子说这种话才不会显得傻。","id":305,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"因为到了很老很老的时候如果还坚持这样想，那就说明他遭遇太多太多了，大地在他身上留下的糟糕痕迹已经不允许他安然度过自己的生活。","id":306,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"......那样的他是活在过去的沙漠中的。如果是我，我甚至没勇气迈出第一步。","id":307,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"要是我那么老又那么傲气，那我走的每一步就都是拿过去的所有事情来戳自己。","id":308,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我甚至想象不出，在那个记忆和过去的沙漠里，人要怎么样才能保证自己还在往前走？","id":309,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"又要是怎么样强韧的精神，才能让他们迈出新的一步，不同于过往的更新的一步？","id":310,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"总觉得你是在暗指谁。","id":312,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我说了，我知道不少他的事，但我确实不认识爱国者老先生。我一句话也没和他说过。","id":314,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"你如果说是他的话，哎，那就是他吧。","id":315,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"假如爱国者老先生......","id":316,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"代入得还挺快。","id":318,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"咳咳。","id":320,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"和他们这些年老的战士不一样，年轻人却是会遗忘，会放弃，会宽恕自己的。","id":321,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"所以，你觉得我只是在为了看得见的一切而战？或者说，这难道不对？","id":323,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"和你在我们离开村子那时候对我说的句子相比，太浅了。","id":325,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"这么几年过来，你已经成了一个优秀的领袖。但这对你也不全是好事，你也不能让自己停在这里吧？","id":326,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"“如果公义需要更多暴力才能伸张，那还能叫公义吗？”","id":327,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"这句话已经困扰我许多年了，这么多年来我一直在想这件事。我可能没想通，但我可是一直在想。","id":328,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"那好，把刚才我们说的命运啊抗争啊这些个词儿全丢掉。阿丽娜老师，今天你想教我们些什么呢？","id":330,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":331},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"嘿。你是不是对霜星也那么油腔滑调的？","id":332,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":333},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"可别瞎说。霜星会把你我的嘴巴都冻上。","id":334,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"如果是你的话，塔露拉，你不会只是为了战胜看得见的敌人去战斗的吧？","id":336,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"纠察队，矿场的监工，追踪着我们的征召兵，乌萨斯医学大臣......战胜那些，我们就胜利了吗？","id":337,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"因为这些东西很坏，所以我们要战胜它？","id":338,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"阿丽娜老师是希望我和看不见的东西战斗。我要怎么战胜它们呢？","id":340,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"和你能许诺的东西，温暖、食物、床被，与这些总有一天能摸得着的东西不一样。","id":342,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"这场仗我们大概不会有结果，我们可能没办法赢。","id":343,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我已经不太想许诺了。太远的事情无异于欺骗。","id":345,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"永远不会赢，那还要打吗？","id":346,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我不是问过吗？到那时候，你还觉得这个命运是值得你去抗争的吗？","id":348,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"这些都过去以后，你甚至连敌人都看不见了。你和那些看不见未来的人有同样的敌人。","id":349,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"......那时，真正的战斗才刚刚开始呢。","id":350,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#3","focus":"2","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"——","id":352,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_npc_078_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你是在说那些精神，那些敌意，还有那些刻在乌萨斯人与我们骨子里的东西。","id":353,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_npc_078_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"——皇帝？","id":354,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/5d/Avg_avg_npc_078_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#3","focus":"1","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"皇帝也只是它的一种样子吧。","id":356,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"只要人们还不肯放下刀，那这场战争就不会结束。","id":357,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我不同意。人们拿起刀去对抗那些倾轧他们的东西是正义的。","id":359,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"没错。其实我认为这场战争，就是不会结束的。","id":361,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"莱塔尼亚和维多利亚的书，托爱国者先生的福，我也看了不少。我很喜欢有些人说的......","id":362,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"“我们的战争是一场针对自我的战争。”","id":363,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"是的，塔露拉，因为你们不会放下手中的刀剑——","id":364,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":365},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......所以你也不会放下手中的针线。","id":366,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":367},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":368},{"type":"image","fadetime":"0","id":369},{"type":"character","id":370},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":371},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","id":372},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"本节课到此结束！已经没什么好教你的了。","id":373,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"孩子们现在就该读书。有的知识他们明天就该知道。","id":374,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"塔露拉......科西切要你是圣人，可人都会犯错。","id":375,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"摔倒以后要爬起来。但如果他不允许你摔倒......","id":376,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"你就只能小心翼翼一点。","id":377,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"面对爱国者也是一样的，我其实不把他和你当成两种人。","id":378,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"你们都已经太相信自己的想法了，我却不能让那些活泼的小生命现在就说，你是对的他是错的这类的话。","id":379,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":380},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"不，阿丽娜。我不能去做我自己都不相信的事情。","id":381,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":382},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"是的，这也是科西切使唤的伎俩。","id":383,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你这不就是在说我没可能消灭他？","id":385,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"那是一种思想。我们可能是没办法消灭一种思想......","id":387,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"但我还是有点自信。","id":388,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"什么自信？","id":390,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":391},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"如果我们那时候都还在你身边的话，我们一定能把你拉回来。","id":392,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"不管科西切的法术是什么样的东西，我们也一定有办法破得掉。我们总能做到。","id":393,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"这场战争，我们从文字和语言开始，从下一刻开始，从一个表情开始。从现在开始。","id":394,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"他们会知道哪种蘑菇可以吃，该怎么养家畜，如果感冒的话要怎么才能早点好。","id":395,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"我们会试着不输掉。","id":396,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":397},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"哈。","id":398,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":399},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"如果是你也一定有机会说服爱国者。","id":400,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"这句我就勉强当是鼓励了。","id":402,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":403},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"喏，缝好了。给她吧。","id":404,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"看得出她很爱惜这件斗篷。像是军队出产的。而且，里三层外三层，看着很大。","id":405,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":406},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"可能是军队的斗篷。也许是......","id":407,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":408},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"啊。","id":409,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":410},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......","id":411,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":412},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"......爱国者先生能继续战斗下去的那些原因，我们说不定找到了其中一个。","id":413,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":414},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"谢谢你，阿丽娜。","id":415,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......等等！","id":416,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/3b/Avg_avg_npc_078.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":417},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"怎么？我要准备明天的课了。这可是绘画课，他们都等着呢。","id":418,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":419},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"下次再帮你弄两把笔刷回来。","id":420,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我是说，我想说......我是想问，你真的......不想和霜星他们认识吗？","id":421,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"战士们都知道我们有好几个感染者老师，只不过你把自己藏得严严实实的......","id":422,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"1","id":423},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"不是现在，塔露拉。","id":424,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"等你说的那个感染者共同的理想实现的时候，我和他们自然会认识的。","id":425,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿丽娜","text":"再说，我们可都是战士，只是战场不同。我们迟早会相互认识的，是不是？","id":426,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/b/b1/Avg_avg_npc_079.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_079","name2":"avg_npc_078#2","focus":"2","id":427},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"没错，阿丽娜。感染者战士阿丽娜。","id":428,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/ec/Avg_avg_npc_078_2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":429},{"type":"blocker","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":430},{"type":"image","id":431}],"characters":["塔露拉","爱国者","霜星","？？？","怯生生的孩子","萨沙","阿丽娜"]}